{
  "stem": "1965.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we, who are now contributing to this wonderful foundation that Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Steven Spielberg has put together-- I feel honored to be here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because as an American, for him to have had the sensitivity to create a foundation like this, I honor him for this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we who have contributed, by choice-- no one told me to do this-- by choice, is because we want to make sure, even though it hurts so deeply inside to relive the experience, that this tragedy, this absolute negativity of the human element, must never repeat itself.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I pray.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sontha, I-- my schooling was very limited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very, very, very limited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no time to educate oneself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would say almost nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was just trying with my mind to find a way to-- how am I going to do today, to be able to go through when you're shaking like this, and you hear the bombs falling, and the, and the, and the, the explosions, and the fires, and the sirens.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every time the siren, and you have to turn all the lights off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you have to run in the basement, and you have no clothes on, and you're shaking from cold, you're shaking from fear.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Education meant nothing, nothing, because you see the mind-- we didn't eat food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't eat brain food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to use our own adrenaline to-- to survive with whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there was no ways to be able to sit and calmly study.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because to study you have to be calm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to be able to concentrate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no concentration here, ability, because it was so hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I read books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Here and there we would look, we'd glance.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
